WEBVTT

00:00:01.994 --> 00:00:23.155
1,600. Yeah, you got your notifications today. I prayed over this a lot last night because of all the people saying, "Hey, they didn't notify me."It bothered me because so many of you would like to be here and YouTube was not telling you.

00:00:23.156 --> 00:00:33.354
We came to the conclusion that because we uploaded three videos yesterday, it notified you every single time.

00:00:33.355 --> 00:00:44.074
I think there's a limit to how many times you can do that so that people can actually be notified. Am I saying that right? Yeah.

00:00:44.075 --> 00:01:02.835
We believe that now we're seeing how many people will get notified to come pray with us versus having three uploads. It was too much. So, we're just going to do this.

00:01:02.836 --> 00:01:13.458
Another thing we found out is that Braden can post on X that we're doing a live, and everybody comes over from X because it notifies you immediately through Elon's.

00:01:13.459 --> 00:01:22.314
I thought that was pretty cool. I thought, "Okay, good thinking,"because the more the merrier, you know.

00:01:22.315 --> 00:01:27.402
Good evening family; good morning, good afternoon wherever you are.

00:01:27.403 --> 00:01:38.818
It's awesome because so many of you from all over the world come and pray with us on a daily basis.

00:01:38.819 --> 00:01:45.139
One person said, "Hey, it's 7:00 in the morning,"and I said, "Wow, that's just awesome.

00:01:45.140 --> 00:01:54.239
Isn't Jesus wonderful?"We're going to go over everything the Lord showed us last night in prayer.

00:01:54.240 --> 00:02:01.577
For those of you who didn't want to watch the beginning, I'll recap what the Lord said yesterday.

00:02:01.578 --> 00:02:08.143
I was in the shower praying and I sat there, just waiting before the Lord.

00:02:08.144 --> 00:02:33.931
He said, "What they don't realize is what you gave them at the beginning of yesterday's video is the key to everything in your Christian walk."He said that will be what will sustain them in ministry and in their walk with Me.

00:02:33.933 --> 00:02:42.799
He said, "Brandon, everyone has a trigger. What sets you off?

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:49.712
What's your boundary when it comes to certain conversations? What irritates you the most?

00:02:49.713 --> 00:03:12.923
What's your trigger?"I asked, "Your trigger?"He said, "Do you know what My trigger is?"I said, "No, Lord."He said, "Touching the glory."He said, "I'll show you scriptures."Jesus says, "I do nothing unless I see My Father.

00:03:12.924 --> 00:03:25.606
Unless I'm instructed by My Father, I do nothing."Everything He did was to give God praise and glory. "I do nothing apart from the Lord.

00:03:25.607 --> 00:03:41.354
Everything that I do in word and in deed, we give all the glory to God."He said, "My trigger, Brandon, what bothers Me the most is touching the glory.

00:03:41.355 --> 00:03:57.518
I will share My glory with no one."I was taken up and I saw Lucifer. He was made for worship.

00:03:57.519 --> 00:04:08.098
Everything about him was glorious as he walked around in heaven leading worship and music. The angels would say, "Oh, you did a good job.

00:04:08.099 --> 00:04:32.678
The worship was just beautiful today."In that praise and acknowledgment, I could see that giving him glory lifted his ego and his pride, taking the glory from the Father.

00:04:32.679 --> 00:04:40.959
He said, "I will exalt myself. I will do all this."Suddenly, he was shot down like lightning.

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:52.072
He touched the glory. He took the praise. The moment he had an ego and started to think, "I'll exalt myself above God. I'll be bigger.

00:04:52.072 --> 00:05:05.811
I'll put my kingdom above His because don't you realize who I am?"he didn't realize the presence was coming from the Father through him to give the Father worship.

00:05:05.812 --> 00:05:22.673
The moment he thought he was something, it changed. Everything we do in ministry, everything we say, everything we impart is not us.

00:05:22.674 --> 00:05:31.868
Me seeing things is not me; it's all to His glory. That's why I said we're the glove.

00:05:31.869 --> 00:05:47.310
We have this glove that's like a snow glove. It's a really cool thing, but it was made to give warmth to the hand.

00:05:47.311 --> 00:05:56.180
The moment the Holy Spirit goes inside of that glove, the human body, it brings life to the glove.

00:05:56.181 --> 00:06:09.218
But the glove is nothing without the Holy Spirit. A human hand goes in there, and the glove is nothing without the hand.

00:06:09.219 --> 00:06:18.959
That's why the Lord was showing me, "Brandon, I'll share My glory with no one in the days ahead."Even more so with what you're about to see.

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:37.043
"If you want longevity in ministry, son, and you want to know My trigger: touch not the glory through the praise of man."People say, "Oh, you're so good.

00:06:37.044 --> 00:06:46.638
You're awesome."But people's opinions change like the water, the weather, and the tide. It always goes back and forth.

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:58.850
He said people's opinions of you will always change—how great they say you are or how great they don't.

00:06:58.851 --> 00:07:08.318
The comment section, the peanut gallery. He was talking to me about finding your box.

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:21.359
What is your box? Like William Seymour, who took his flesh and told it to shut up. As I told you all yesterday, what's your box?

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:40.131
William Seymour sat in the front of the stage with a box on his head for sometimes 45 minutes to an hour before the service would even start as a display of humility so that He gets the glory.

00:07:40.132 --> 00:07:52.559
Regardless of what happens in this vast auditorium, He gets the glory, the honor, and the praise.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:08:00.010
"I'll share My glory with no one."In the days ahead, you'll see this more and more.

00:08:00.011 --> 00:08:22.318
He said, "As long, Brandon, as you decrease so that I increase, we'll get along just fine."Basically, He wants to use people in a great capacity, but everyone has a trigger.

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:48.613
What's your trigger? When you get to know the Father more intimately, you realize there are boundaries with His triggers—what He loves and what He doesn't.

00:08:48.614 --> 00:08:54.879
So I sit before Him and listen as He talks to me about what's coming.

00:08:54.880 --> 00:09:13.919
He tells me about finances, the president, what's coming after the attack with Venezuela, what's happening next for China, and what's coming for Taiwan.

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:25.185
You learn these things as you sit at His feet and die to yourself. That's why you die daily. What are you dying to? Self.

00:09:25.186 --> 00:09:32.398
When the anointing's on me and the cloak comes on, I'm just that glove.

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:41.534
The moment it moves out after the livestream's over, I'm just as helpless as anyone.

00:09:41.535 --> 00:09:48.420
When that anointing is on, you feel like Superman and the glory is there.

00:09:48.421 --> 00:10:02.646
But the Lord said impartations, healings, and manifestations like you wouldn't believe are about to come to this planet. We're about to see things we've always dreamed of seeing.

00:10:02.647 --> 00:10:20.897
He said, "There's a difference between being a general in an army and being one of the foot soldiers."You can be a general in His army for what's coming, though all of us are important and have a position.

00:10:20.898 --> 00:10:31.177
The foot soldiers are just as important as the generals, but the general has a lot more responsibility. To whom much is given, much is required.

00:10:31.178 --> 00:10:43.919
General Flynn and all the generals we've had in our military had a lot more responsibility, and if they messed up, it cost a lot of lives.

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:56.078
So, they have to be on target and precise with what they are hearing from the commander-in-chief of the United States of America, our president, right?

00:10:56.079 --> 00:11:04.032
You distribute the message to the people and they help bring out the call and we win battles.

00:11:04.033 --> 00:11:10.099
The Lord said, Brandon, there is a lot of difference between generals and privates and lieutenants and all that.

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:20.958
It is interesting, so you learn the chain of command and you learn a lot of things as I grow, and he instructs me all the time.

00:11:20.959 --> 00:11:31.999
This is what you are going to do and this is what you are not going to do, and I want you to do it precisely. Yes, sir.

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:45.359
So, as I sat before him today, he said, I want you to tell my people again, humble themselves underneath the mighty hand of God. Humble yourself.

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:57.039
No matter what your potter's wheel experience is, no matter what you are going through, you do not have to announce it on Facebook.

00:11:57.040 --> 00:12:04.398
You do not have to tell everybody your business. You know, I am on the potter's wheel right now and everything is so rough.

00:12:04.399 --> 00:12:11.200
You know how many times I went on Facebook and told everybody about me?

00:12:11.201 --> 00:12:19.560
I never once told anybody how bad my day was, other than my grandmother across the street, of how rough some days were.

00:12:19.561 --> 00:12:27.439
I did not even tell my mom and my dad. Nobody knew other than her because she lived across the street.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:32.398
But I did not make an announcement on Facebook so everybody would pray for me.

00:12:32.399 --> 00:12:38.884
I did not tell every sister so and so how much I was going through because I wanted them to feel sorry for me and give me finances.

00:12:38.885 --> 00:12:44.784
Do not give ministry of hints. Well, you know, we are having a hard time financially.

00:12:44.785 --> 00:12:51.534
I have got ten dollars left, five dollars left. I did not make the announcement so that people would still feel sorry for me.

00:12:51.535 --> 00:13:00.372
I thought if God can provide and God knows how much I need, I do not need sister so and so or brother so and so to try to meet that need.

00:13:00.373 --> 00:13:09.359
Either God does it or he is not God. But ministry of hints is not God.

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:20.479
Well, you know, won't you help me? I have got my bills going to be cut off this next week. Ministry of hints is not God.

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:29.959
Keep your mouth shut, and if you have sowed and you have tithed and you have given, keep your eyes on him, not on man.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:43.518
The moment man becomes your provider you are in trouble. The moment man becomes your need maker, the way maker, you are in trouble.

00:13:43.519 --> 00:13:58.770
I do not need a miracle behind my mailbox. I need Jesus. That is why Diana's dream, when she had the dream, the lady was looking at her and the glory was on us and she said, Oh, don't you see?

00:13:58.771 --> 00:14:08.114
It is just Jesus. When people see you in the days ahead and your face is shining with glory, it is not about you.

00:14:08.115 --> 00:14:14.958
The world is going to be attracted to it and the blessings flow through it.

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:21.278
Increase comes from it. But that is not the focus. The focus is Jesus.

00:14:21.279 --> 00:14:29.759
And the glory will be on you, ladies and gentlemen, for what I have seen. A level of the glory that we have never seen before.

00:14:29.760 --> 00:14:46.078
And when we go into the Walmarts and the Targets and the Sam's or Costco or wherever you go shopping and they see that glory on you, it is just Jesus.

00:14:46.079 --> 00:15:00.223
You always deflect to him. You must know this. I told Braden and Diana and Paisley today, I said, this is God's trigger.

00:15:00.224 --> 00:15:09.518
This is so important. And to the point that I am turning off the comment section. It is not about Brandon.

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:19.679
This is not about how great Brandon is or how much he hears or what he does not hear and the egg throwers or the praise or the palm leaf people.

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:27.679
This is just me being obedient to what God has called me to do and what he has called me to say. And if I miss it, I miss it. And that is between me and him.

00:15:27.680 --> 00:15:37.039
Or if it is right and I pray it is, you know, I do not want to cause any prophetic confusion, but it is always to give glory to him.

00:15:37.040 --> 00:15:54.398
Die to yourself. Die to yourself. I saw it today. I have heard people say it a thousand times and I thought what are they truly saying until it became Rhema to me.

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:59.409
You can parrot things so much and I hear somebody, I heard a parrot one time.

00:15:59.410 --> 00:16:09.604
Oh Lord we give you all the glory and honor and praise, but yet they display something so much haughtiness upon them on the platform.

00:16:09.605 --> 00:16:23.837
So much pride, so much pride, and you see it and it is so much about attracting the glory to them as they move in the gift but yet you see the gift and you say, is it right?

00:16:23.838 --> 00:16:36.693
Are you right right now? No, it is so much about you. But when I see Katherine, she was always back, she did that thing and the Lord said, learn, I will share my glory with no one.

00:16:36.694 --> 00:16:47.341
You see, there is a lot of parrots that know how to parrot and copy what you have seen on the stage.

00:16:47.342 --> 00:16:58.719
There is a lot of parrots versus the ones that are really truly sold out and they are dead to it.

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:03.954
And the Lord said, I am going to pour out my spirit on another level on people.

00:17:03.955 --> 00:17:18.479
Brandon, you are about to see some glorious things, but touch not the anointing. Don't ever take it and ever be arrogant.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:25.198
Humble yourself before me and I will flow through you and we will get along just fine.

00:17:25.199 --> 00:17:31.310
I say all this stuff to you to try to help you. Maybe it does, maybe it doesn't.

