But you are excited about the Ferrari and you are showing everybody and you are taking Instagram photos and look at me.

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:17.082
Cool car, and the Lord said, That ain't your Ferrari, son. You are borrowing the keys for the moment.

00:18:17.083 --> 00:18:25.519
That ain't your car. You are a pretender. You have no business answering questions.

00:18:25.520 --> 00:18:39.279
It is not your gift. You are borrowing it for that time. Don't ever do that again. I said I will bow my head before you. Father, I am sorry.

00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:48.079
What do you ever think that you have the ability to answer anybody's question on there unless I tell you to say something?

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:57.283
I, that is haughtiness. Don't ever do that again. I said I had no argument.

00:18:57.284 --> 00:19:04.388
It is a hard thing. It is like a stomach punch whenever I come before you and I just humble.

00:19:04.389 --> 00:19:09.678
I just like, and I am not wanting sister clipboard to come and say Brandon, you said this, you said that.

