When you see the dead raised in front of you and the media wants to put you all over the news, remember that you are the glove.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:29.918
Apart from him, you can do nothing. You did not do nothing. You are just the glove.

00:20:29.919 --> 00:20:36.407
You will see the dead raised in the days ahead. You are going to see the blind eyes open. You are going to see ears open.

00:20:36.408 --> 00:20:45.411
You are going to see things that there is going to be shock and awe on Instagram, Facebook, the dead were raised.

00:20:45.412 --> 00:20:54.158
Did you see who did it? No, you did not do nothing. You were just the glove.

00:20:54.159 --> 00:21:08.558
So, I am trying to prepare you for what is about to come. Take not the glory for what is about to come, ladies and gentlemen.

00:21:08.559 --> 00:21:19.119
