00:26:15.919 --> 00:26:27.359
Apart from me, Brandon, they can do nothing, but they think it's them.'And that's pride.

00:26:27.360 --> 00:26:38.399
From the great jobs that you have—corporate offices, CEOs—it rains on the just and the unjust.

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:43.873
